{"tid":1272253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個話衝 一定要有leader？","createTime":"2019-07-01T09:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T10:20:38.000Z","uid":171139,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"345942021068241acf0b3e55c7b6888238d492a7","tid":1272253,"uid":171139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:52:44.000Z","msg":"仲發緊夢 依家去痾過夜尿繼續發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日我晏晝出到立法會<br />\n一大班人企係立法會2號定3號門口（晏晝1點爆個對）<br />\n無野做 個情況膠住左好耐<br />\n<br />\n跟住有對男女聊我傾偈<br />\n佢話依家呢個情況就算企落去都無用<br />\n不如搵一部分人去打遊擊<br />\n爆埋1號門口（即係正門） 分散警力<br />\n<br />\n因為我地都係自發義士 無入tg group<br />\n唔識召集人 無咩政黨背景 無召集力<br />\n遊行人士全部都係添美道行一轉就走<br />\n<br />\n個陣我去左抖氣 抖完氣發現個對男女拎住兩條鐵柱去到1號門口<br />\n真係得佢地兩個<br />\n於是我就上前再同佢搭話<br />\n或者無經深思熟慮 或者會比連登仔屌<br />\n屌我地地咁做有咩意義<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知 但我選擇左加把手<br />\n由兩對手 五對手 十對手 幾十對手<br />\n現場無人篤灰 無人話我地係鬼<br />\n只係聽到一句「香港人加油」<br />\n愈黎愈多人 連遊行人士都加入埋<br />\n逼爆成個立法會1號正門<br />\n最後成功爆左1號正門<br />\n<br />\n其實有心<br />\n每個人都可以係leader<br />\n每個人都可以係梁天琦<br />\n只要有個道火<br />\n就算聲音幾細<br />\n都可以做得多<br />\n<br />\n未出黎/係側邊旁觀既人<br />\n一齊加入我地<br />\n打倒呢個政府<br />\n就算做既野有幾咁微不足道<br />\n幾咁渺小<br />\n都會有人睇到聽到<br />\n<br />\n我要繼續發夢啦 暫時覆唔到大家<br />\n如果大家唔認可我地做既野 歡迎你地係到留言<br />\n發完夢我一定會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da359470daac640cefbc8c1fe22d6fbab1a80fe3","tid":1272253,"uid":171139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:53:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8fa72d2c3e5e361c56c193b2803303b8cfadff6a","tid":1272253,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:54:11.000Z","msg":"加油！"},{"pid":"f2b7d8cfa71b3b1b7912b8d9ffaacad86e32fc17","tid":1272253,"uid":111899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:55:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"935d0364fd7971e6b19e119a5ce3dedaba3845ba","tid":1272253,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:55:38.000Z","msg":"過往已經試過有leader既抗爭<br />\n結果只係不斷消磨士氣同精力<br />\n而家自發性行動反而更有機動性同效率, 可以按時現場情況即時做出合適行動"},{"pid":"243f8d1273e793e0a0be50b67d95b73f72aacb5c","tid":1272253,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87307f43dcd8cd99539b33661504e06ca72d671","tid":1272253,"uid":224075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:56:15.000Z","msg":"加油啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a63c1697869f486229a64163f9d2ced7b083661","tid":1272253,"uid":191989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:56:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df9522fabf1071c6bbc345d3355caeec4e82e4bf","tid":1272253,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:57:15.000Z","msg":"Take care"},{"pid":"b9cb5c789f05010166afe692f49c27d7ef11f64b","tid":1272253,"uid":47776,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:57:39.000Z","msg":"樓豬一定無加手<br />\n你都係睇住人做架姐係唔係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依啲咁暴力嘅野點會發生係全港最親中嘅論壇上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dea9e7e13af30a9786643eb5742107be2f14932","tid":1272253,"uid":265786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98825e3597f3226f6460b23d7e4b1e68d680b31f","tid":1272253,"uid":192776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:01:31.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"06cd994989a93b91b6369d0ebb517ede5f0a9452","tid":1272253,"uid":212119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:13:13.000Z","msg":"萬事小心"},{"pid":"5445d6e49ef714c4d5570761ab27196db0c49756","tid":1272253,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:20:38.000Z","msg":"Support 根本係要衝擊下個政府<br />\n屌你老母 咁撚多人都唔聽下市民聲音"}]}